Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.79,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0}Ever since that day passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:46.01,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,500)\pos(640,710)}I promised myself that I'd never cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.59,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0}But even while I hoarded up the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:56.64,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,1000)}there was something I couldn't forgive myself for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:00.19,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I'll never be able
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.69,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}to return to those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.78,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I'm still powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:12.99,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I watch as the shards of memories disappear, one by one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.83,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,1000}memories of when you were still with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.88,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I long to become
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.67,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}stronger than I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:29.80,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}so that my voice will eventually reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.14,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}If the wind happens to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.89,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}in the midst of my long journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:39.52,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,1000)}I'll look up at the sky in search of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:46.86,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,1000)}Beyond the daybreak, a ray of light breaks free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:52.41,ED05 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,1000)}A rainbow spans across the sky.
