Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President has returned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.21,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he destroyed a tank from Briggs at the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.51,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,That'll show those monkeys from Briggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.22,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather the rest of the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.72,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,We need to recapture mission headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.01,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.72,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President is at the main gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:08.94,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.40,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time seeing him with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:21.07,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the one who ripped off my granddaughter's arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.91,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:33.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So you were planning on sacrificing all the civilians\Nso that you high-level officials would gain immortality,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.21,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and unify the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.09,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Is Führer President Bradley doing everything\Neven with the knowledge of what you all are up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.01,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,He's the leader of this country,\Nand was made for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.52,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.52,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,We're planning on creating a world without war!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.15,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying the world should be destroyed once for that purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.74,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not destruction, but rather regeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.62,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the 'reconstruction' stage that you alchemists refer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.95,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,The civilians aren't going to be given 'death'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.12,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to receive the honor of living within us forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.13,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,And we're going to unify the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.63,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,All is one, and one is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:20.34,Default,Edi,0000,0000,0000,,We, the chosen ones of Amestris, will become one and-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.14,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.52,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What will you guys do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.52,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to gain everything for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.52,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come along with me, you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:38.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll ask that man to-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:49.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier, so I must obey the orders of my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, I don't know what to believe anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hesitating in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:03.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Obeying a superior you can't even believe doesn't make you loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're just fooling yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:16.02,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just choose a way of living that won't shame your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.95,Default,Eric,0000,0000,0000,,I have family in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.58,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.75,Default,Gus,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.64,Default,Cas,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.77,Default,Eric,0000,0000,0000,,this is our answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.03,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Mission headquarters, what's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.20,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Not too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.24,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Soldiers have begun to recover in several areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.41,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.79,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.75,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,And the survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been able to get in touch with our men who are around the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's a high possibility that there are many Central Soldiers surrounding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.80,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If things get dangerous over there, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.64,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.02,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:37.69,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this place has become filled with enemies again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.73,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until the Central Soldiers form up and storm this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.61,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.37,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,After going down a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.96,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dig a side tunnel as an escape route, just like I did when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.00,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we escape together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.05,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You all could probably use some time to recover and plan, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.28,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You two can sense him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's more of a "bad feeling".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like the feeling you get when a bad scar starts aching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.69,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, do I have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.90,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.99,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.58,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.25,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,The man who created King Bradley...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.38,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.88,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you're on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.10,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:42.35,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were at the radio station,\Nbut you actually took the effort to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:46.36,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for giving me one less thing to do, Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.24,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, entertain them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Dolls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.46,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.38,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Their movements clearly differ from the dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.63,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,They're men who might have become King Bradley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.18,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They were gathered as soon as they were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,and they were given special education and training
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,for the sole purpose of becoming the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:27.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And with the twelfth experiment, King Bradley was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.69,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So these are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.49,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,The leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:38.33,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, they've been training for battle all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.04,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Although they're not as powerful as King Bradley,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.79,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,they're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...those rebels...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.87,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.62,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.55,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to pull it out, I'd probably die from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.14,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.52,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.02,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident, youn-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.94,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, prey like you gets my heart pumping faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:27.14,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you put up such a good fight despite being more aged than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.73,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.49,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.41,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,The prince from Xing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.67,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.67,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Quit taking over without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:59.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like the girl who cut her own arm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:04.43,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Just like her, you endanger your life for something you can't throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.56,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.77,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer fight. Just throw me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.10,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.31,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to become a man like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.61,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,A king exists for his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.15,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Without his people, there is no king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.70,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning on abandoning the people of his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.74,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not someone I want to become!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.71,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,A man unworthy of being called 'king', huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.88,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Then we must defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.69,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.94,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.94,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I shall rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.48,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Harden, Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.82,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the young master's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.20,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:05.87,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.45,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:15.63,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for this old geezer to begin his eternal rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.30,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!!{make sure you time both of these; it's important! ~koki}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.30,Default-alt,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.97,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming to hell with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.60,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:47.82,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give him a single wound, even by risking my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.66,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.71,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.42,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you possess the eyes of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:08.93,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,you can't possibly dodge an attack coming from somewhere you can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:15.31,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, I'll... be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.69,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,to hell with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.65,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.02,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.95,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.78,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,First you get stuck in a ditch,\Nthen you ram into a lightpost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.95,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,You really suck at driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.12,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.91,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful that we were able to get this far in a beat up car like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far! Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to hurry up and find a place where we can get underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.81,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.64,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:57.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How non-human can your movements get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.78,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, your back is wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I've entrusted my back to, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The gate of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.75,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Human transmutation, a taboo in alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:53.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists who try it end up opening the gate of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.97,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,paying a befitting toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:03.19,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how the Elric Brothers sacrificed their bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:04.65,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.28,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They took a bit of my insides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.07,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But what I learned from all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:20.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,is that human transmutation never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:28.38,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, soldiers like yourselves probably aren't interested in tales like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.26,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:36.80,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who have opened the gate of truth are the "human sacrifices" they speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You may have a handhold in finding out what they are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.10,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So you all had someone you wanted to see again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.94,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,even if you had to open the gate of truth and sacrifice your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.70,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have someone that you'd give up anything for just to see again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.79,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's something that means nothing to a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.75,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Having regret for the deceased is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.75,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,We fight in order to keep them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.22,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.85,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel like I understand something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.35,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.23,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met him, I threatened him and told him to tell me everything he knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:33.86,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,but that boy didn't say a word about his old friend having been taken hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.57,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Just one line:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.49,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,"Please try to realize."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:43.04,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes were different from those of us soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:48.29,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,or even those of State Alchemists,\Nwho are referred to as the dogs of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:55.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say, they were eyes that didn't want to lose anything important to them again no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes of an unreasonable child?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.35,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said that those straightforward eyes didn't move my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:15.28,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,But will those naïvely honest feelings of his\Nfind a way out of the difficulty in this fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.36,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,or will they come back to harm him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.53,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.58,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.67,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Number 16,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.92,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Number 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.92,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Number 21,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.43,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Number 23, Number 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.05,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:43.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.19,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.91,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:15.59,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many alchemy research facilities under direct control of the Führer President exist in Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There should be four that are currently being used...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Research Laboratory 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There are five!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A transmutation circle with five points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:40.03,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the curving underground path was a circle that connects the research facilities?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Heinkel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.36,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.20,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like this is a good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.87,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to dig a hole for escape purposes in this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is where we say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.80,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,We still need to remain here and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:47.22,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out is probably the enemy's backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:51.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just let our chance to ambush them go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.39,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.53,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.66,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,We're in your debt, Izumi Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I should be saying that, Major General Arm-
